comments: Thompson (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Temple (CHI) and absorbs the contact.  The two players briefly engage following the screen.
Temple (CHI) places his arms against Thompson (BOS) but does not dislodge him from his position as he reaches for the long rebound.
Pritchard (BOS) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Williams (CHI) during his shot attempt at the basket.
White (CHI) is not established in a legal guarding position in Pritchard's (BOS) path and he trips him, affecting his drive to the basket.
Langford (BOS) briefly has an arm around Theis' (CHI) waist but he immediately slides it off without affecting his FOM.
Langford (BOS) legally contests Temple's (CHI) shot attempt at the basket.
Brown (BOS) and White (CHI) come together at the same spot and incidental contact occurs before White steals the pass.
Brown (BOS) moves toward Williams' (CHI) space and marginal contact occurs.
Williams (CHI) does not initiate any contact with Brown (BOS) as he attempts to protect the ball.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
As both Temple (CHI) and Waters (BOS) go for the loose ball, incidental contact occurs.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a jump ball stands.
Williams (BOS) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
Theis (CHI) moves into Tatum (BOS) and makes contact to the body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Waters (BOS) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
Theis (CHI) is in a legal guarding position and the marginal contact is initiated by Tatum (BOS) during his drive to the basket.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Celtics possession is overturned to Bulls possession.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Temple (CHI).
